{"tid":1144670,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"A股跌近6%差絕全球 內媒封殺貿易戰消息","createTime":"2019-05-08T08:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T11:37:52.000Z","uid":117934,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"445250054bc2d8b54ee7030e15180ec8d3760451","tid":1144670,"uid":117934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:15:43.000Z","msg":"上海綜合指數今日（6日）跌5.6%，深圳成份股指數跌7.6%，為全球表現最差指數。但對於造成大跌市的罪魁禍首，特朗普在貿易談判突然反口，內地傳媒和所有財經網站，由昨晚凌晨特朗普宣佈提高中國關稅，到今日A股三點收市後，都隻字不提，只以「受消息衝擊、特大事件」來解釋，令許多股民對股市大跌摸不著頭腦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BtPsk1s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBtPsk1s.png&h=9b904a13&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當新華社於A股收市後出稿，一眾傳媒陸續發出消息，但只引述外交部回應指，「下一輪中美經貿磋商：中方團隊正準備赴美磋商，爭取達成互利雙贏的協定。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/io4zLs7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fio4zLs7.png&h=ea298692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年6月起，中宣部已下達「封口令」，在新華社發出通稿，即中央對事件定調定性之前，所有傳媒不得報道任何關於中美貿易戰消息。金融市場瞬息萬變，當局封殺資訊猶如掩耳盜鈴，反而更加劇市場恐慌，今日A股全日越跌越深。有內地網民在網上及微信紛紛求救，請教其他網友，「怎麼會跌成這樣，有利麼利空（利淡）消息嗎」，「是誰在打壓中國股市」。"},{"pid":"294d4a7bf1c67b2bbd356c4f8a8f2d9432098de8","tid":1144670,"uid":68,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:18:46.000Z","msg":"咁又點 都唔會爆架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2223e78349c8f71473e5df373abdc3c397a7ddb","tid":1144670,"uid":171446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:20:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75ccbdfd411e5d96e737b39bed553333450006b3","tid":1144670,"uid":117934,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T08:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q1nQ3hW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq1nQ3hW.png&h=c66387f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b85b2b56de16a6356b5cb2579ccc1832001ed7b7","tid":1144670,"uid":4256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/08/191428_f3b8c10cd3ccde7bb4b3ce2f8bfea0f5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F08%2F191428_f3b8c10cd3ccde7bb4b3ce2f8bfea0f5.png&h=52b4a03d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d23768e6dfd49d415b2bda6b7374e0d32a2eb664","tid":1144670,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:16:10.000Z","msg":"訓撚醒未 今日跌幾多呀"},{"pid":"e683f1b30be5842fe28f1ba1df4a37de01f456ed","tid":1144670,"uid":53397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:37:52.000Z","msg":"大6  不停印銀紙rmb 無限金錢   除非變廢紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}